  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00168', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-114-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當服務對象不知道要去那裡求助，社會工作者協助連結需要的服務是下列何種角色的發揮？', '["教育者（educator）", "倡導者（advocate）", "評估者（evaluator）", "中介者（broker）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b3770e8743a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e496b24c7c76", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "505", "s": "0404", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00169', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-114-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '預先因應工作結束所可能產生的失落、焦慮等情緒，協助案主確認自我的能力，並能持續維持穩定的生活 狀態。這段敘述是屬於下列何種社會工作階段最主要的任務？', '["建立關係階段", "擬訂計畫階段", "計畫實施階段", "結案階段"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b3770e8743a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e496b24c7c76", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "505", "s": "0404", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00170', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-114-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '我曾經也和你一樣面臨家庭照顧的抉擇，那個時候我覺得非常的無助。這段敘述屬於下列何種會談技巧？', '["同理心", "自我揭露", "尊重", "面質"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b3770e8743a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e496b24c7c76", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "505", "s": "0404", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00171', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-114-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作者會談重點著重於特定的目的，並且期望對於案主所遭遇的議題有更全面的瞭解，據此引導服務 介入的方向。這是屬於下列何種會談類型？', '["診斷與決策會談", "治療性會談", "資訊或社會史會談", "預估（assessment）會談"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b3770e8743a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e496b24c7c76", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "505", "s": "0404", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00172', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-114-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種情境中，專業的工作關係之間發生了情感反轉移的狀況？', '["案主覺得社會工作者很貼心的為自己設想，因此十分感謝社會工作者的協助", "社會工作者在工作的過程中，很在意自己是否能夠提供適切的服務", "在工作的過程中，社會工作者發覺案主的行為表現就像自己的妹妹一樣，做事十分不負責任，因此常會 對案主感到氣憤", "案主很信任社會工作者，願意完全配合社會工作者所提供的服務計畫"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b3770e8743a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e496b24c7c76", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "505", "s": "0404", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
